  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with drug-resistant epilepsy

          -  Age of 18 years or more

          -  Follow-up in the epilepsy unit at Pitié-Salpêtrière Hospital

          -  Before or after the presurgical evaluation unit including a video-EEG monitoring, a
             structural brain imaging and a full neuropsychological assessment

          -  Covered by a social security system

          -  Signing of consent form

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Persons under guardianship, curatorship or any other administrative or judicial
             deprivation of rights and freedom

          -  Refusal to consent form

          -  Contraindications to MRI

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Refusal to be informed in the case of detection of an abnormality during the
             experiment
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
